{"tid":710013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇人提] 聽日係一年一度嘅玉林狗肉節，又係大愛撚食狗撚互屌時候","createTime":"2018-06-20T12:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T17:03:46.000Z","uid":123613,"like":25,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"32e3cef566bf7cfcabe09012ec254b28432acc56","tid":710013,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:16:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180620/58342275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180620%2F58342275&d=GNMrYXnoROGLfIcRfWQGKZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=56df1c5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180620%2F58342275&h=68fbe0c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180620/58342275</a><br />\n <br />\n【玉林狗肉節直擊】貴婦狗都劏！$60加工代宰 主人帶狗齊齊食<br />\n2小時前61.5K<br />\n即時兩岸<br />\n <br />\n明日夏至，狗肉節再臨。《蘋果》記者親赴廣西玉林直擊，只見市面周街有賣荔枝攤檔，狗肉店雖然被當局責令換成香肉字眼，但大型狗肉店晚市連宵夜時段仍座無虛席，更過份的是有人竟拖寵物狗前往吃狗肉！<br />\n<br />\n此外，往年當街棒殺狗隻和劏狗的血腥場面今年已不復見，不過，知情人對記者表示，狗狗殺戮場只是轉到隱蔽的劏宰場。而記者到位於玉林北流鎮松花村的一個劏狗場直擊，發現該處停着幾車待宰狗兒，不時傳出悲鳴叫聲。屠宰場外寫着提供本地狗批發和零售，店主稱：「今日買28元人民幣（下同‧約34港元）斤，明天（夏至）就要30（約36.3港元）。」買劏好的要提前3個多小時下單，「太多人買，忙不過來」。<br />\n<br />\n記者在附近觀察時，正好有一名戴黑超男子，在車尾廂運來一隻疑似貴婦犬，花50元（約60港元）叫工人代為宰殺。只見狗狗瑟縮在寵中，沒有一點神氣。被困鐵籠和車尾廂多時的牠，似乎意識到危險，在被抬下車時想往後退，但被困籠中，無路可逃。記者問黑超男子是自已養的嗎？他不答話，與工人合力抬狗入屠宰場。<br />\n<br />\n記者一度想繞道農田到後福拍攝，但有負責監視的男子對外來人相當警惕，見記者站路邊舉手機拍攝，即上前查問。記者問他屠宰場情況，他即警愓地驅趕記者離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知咁多位連登仔支唔支持狗肉節呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反對=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3300c4d7793583bcf446e24c87b2fd44e4c66785","tid":710013,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d702746b9cb47123ee4ad80206b07b105ff84c17","tid":710013,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:19:44.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"8604f827137a163b753a42551f0d8169d81d3e8c","tid":710013,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b24d9ab8c67c15fffeb93edfe83bcd13eebdd882","tid":710013,"uid":189453,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:37:38.000Z","msg":"唔係話支持 但我亦唔會反對佢"},{"pid":"4777b1a137df9eb9e569632b37d4175bd48f26e0","tid":710013,"uid":41813,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:41:14.000Z","msg":"支持狗肉節<br />\n亦支持偷人隻狗死全家"},{"pid":"18b2a5d45797b5da384d4d4fb4068f1f36ebe844","tid":710013,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:42:23.000Z","msg":"道德左膠俾人劏埋就最撚好"},{"pid":"f91a9b7a3c34fde106df19fbda52d42697c7c9e5","tid":710013,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:46:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af6f45abab468d100793f2a98ce122074780b999","tid":710013,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T12:51:31.000Z","msg":"老衲名言:<br />\n大家都係愛狗人士, 左膠愛生的, 老衲愛熟的"},{"pid":"8e242adb5336ea31cf8573a259d0272422faea85","tid":710013,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87644b3e517709afa2c74b83574171e42ba20e73","tid":710013,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"幾時有牛肉節，雞肉節，豬肉節 ?"},{"pid":"44afe59ca63cc1eaa709b905cd6430fd5fe1934d","tid":710013,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87644b3e517709afa2c74b83574171e42ba20e73","tid":710013,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"幾時有牛肉節，雞肉節，豬肉節 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:53:55.000Z","msg":"幾時有人肉節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b83a4af916178273b01cb0ca133ef942e25d0e4","tid":710013,"uid":178332,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T16:04:09.000Z","msg":"屌佢但又食其他動物肉嘅人同Trump冇分別<br />\n明嘅人就會明<br />\n一切歧視嘅根源都係一樣<br />\n利申：反對食用任何動物"},{"pid":"cb590445132e66c849c5dec675c3a6edd40de6d8","tid":710013,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T16:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30ea5af95fb82c74c44eba383965398b307572c","tid":710013,"uid":72186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:02:14.000Z","msg":"食貓重好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見連登成日都有貓奴po佢哋啲貓上嚟<br />\n隻隻都好好味噉"},{"pid":"a277cf29037728b5806e4b17f5d830271d077bd0","tid":710013,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}